<p t="107" d="1334" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">This one time,​</p>
<p t="1976" d="3804" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">I was playing the piano
in my high school&#39;s music room.​</p>
<p t="5780" d="3203" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">That&#39;s when I heard this scream out of nowhere!​</p>
<p t="8983" d="2235" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">It scared me out of my boots.​</p>
<p t="11218" d="3136" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">So I looked in that direction,
but I couldn&#39;t see anything clearly.​</p>
<p t="15523" d="1967" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">It remains a mystery to this day.​</p>
<p t="23431" d="2134" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">Thanks for listening.​</p>
<p t="26267" d="2735" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Oh, there&#39;s one left still.​</p>
<p t="29870" d="3037" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">If you blow out the last candle during
ghost stories, one really appears.​</p>
<p t="32907" d="400" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">What?​</p>
<p t="33307" d="2968" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">I&#39;m going to be too scared
to go to the washroom alone.​</p>
<p t="38079" d="1201" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">I&#39;ll go turn on the lights.​</p>
<p t="39280" d="1601" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Th-Thank you.​</p>
<p t="40881" d="1802" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">That went on for ages.​</p>
<p t="42683" d="1869" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">I was so scared.​</p>
<p t="44552" d="4304" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">But I had fun hanging out with Sora-senpai,
since it&#39;s been a while.​</p>
<p t="48856" d="1802" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">Man, I&#39;m starving now.​</p>
<p t="50658" d="1335" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Wanna cook something?​</p>
<p t="51993" d="1935" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">That sounds good and all,​</p>
<p t="53928" d="3403" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">but didn&#39;t Miko-chan and someone
go out on snack run?​</p>
<p t="57331" d="2636" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">I bet they got scared and ran away!​</p>
<p t="59967" d="1700" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Maybe, yeah.​</p>
<p t="66674" d="2169" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">The lights aren&#39;t coming on.​</p>
<p t="68843" d="1433" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">Aren&#39;t the switches right there?​</p>
<p t="79487" d="734" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">Sora-senpai!​</p>
