<p t="81355" d="1068" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">Whoa!​</p>
<p t="82423" d="901" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">You blew it out!​</p>
<p t="83324" d="1868" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">You blew out the last candle!​</p>
<p t="85192" d="2436" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">You&#39;re too afraid of this.​</p>
<p t="87628" d="2836" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">I&#39;m more worried about Sora-senpai, really.​</p>
<p t="90464" d="2736" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">The lights aren&#39;t coming on,
and she isn&#39;t coming back.​</p>
<p t="93200" d="1268" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Shall we go look for her?​</p>
<p t="94468" d="1302" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">I don&#39;t wanna.​</p>
<p t="95770" d="1935" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">C&#39;mon, or we&#39;ll leave you behind.​</p>
<p t="97705" d="1200" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">I want that even less!​</p>
<p t="100808" d="3936" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">S-Sora-senpai? Are you there?​</p>
<p t="106680" d="2703" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">Sorry, did I scare you too badly?​</p>
<p t="109383" d="1769" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">The lights just wouldn&#39;t come on.​</p>
<p t="111152" d="1600" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">A blackout?​</p>
<p t="113454" d="2035" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">Yeah, so I went looking for this flashlight.​</p>
<p t="115489" d="566" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">Oh.​</p>
<p t="117925" d="968" wp="1" ws="1" p="3">Eek!​</p>
<p t="118893" d="1568" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">Y-You okay?​</p>
<p t="120461" d="1134" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Sora-senpai?​</p>
<p t="121595" d="1502" wp="1" ws="1" p="22">We&#39;re back!​</p>
<p t="123097" d="1902" wp="1" ws="1" p="22">And we brought snacks!​</p>
<p t="124999" d="1401" wp="1" ws="1" p="22">Uh, what are you doing?​</p>
<p t="126400" d="701" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Huh?​</p>
<p t="127101" d="2102" wp="1" ws="1" p="2">Well, Sora-senpai just...​</p>
<p t="129203" d="1500" wp="1" ws="1" p="1">What&#39;s this about me?​</p>
<p t="131372" d="2000" wp="1" ws="1" p="4">When did you get outside?​</p>
<p t="134208" d="2601" wp="1" ws="1" p="22">She was with me, shopping the entire time.​</p>
